data.description: Discover comfort and convenience in this meticulously maintained 3-bed, 2.5-bath home in the desirable Poquoson area! This home, just 14 years young, boasts a brand-new dishwasher, beautiful new kitchen countertops, and a luxurious primary suite with a soaking tub and shower. Step outside to your backyard oasis, complete with a fire pit, patio, and a beautifully landscaped yard great for relaxation and gatherings. This home is a stone's throw away from a tranquil park and offers seamless access to nearby shopping, military bases, highways, and more. Don't miss the chance to make this pristine Poquoson home yours! Ask your agent about the transferable home warranty and HVAC maintenance program for added peace of mind.  Ask about assuming a VA loan at 4.5%!
